<plot>Michele Basta creates life-sized sculptures that she animates using stop-motion film techniques. Arachne is a blend of the artists' personal recollections and experiences along with ancient legends and folktales that come together to create a hybrid, personal mythology. A narrative translated through allegory, riddle and metaphor, this film will allow you to traverse deeper realms of mystery, beauty and the grotesque.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?044462</url></doc>
